<li>Newby, Richard, <i>Kill Now, Talk Forever: Debating Sacco and Vanzetti</i>, (2002) <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0759607923" class="internal">ISBN 0759607923</a></li>
<li>Feuerlicht, Roberta Strauss, <i>Justice Crucified, The Story of Sacco and Vanzetti</i>, McGraw-Hill Book Company, 1977.</li>
